# Tennoplan — Cursor Project Rules

## Project Overview
Tennoplan is a free, open-source Warframe endgame tracker web app.
Live at: tennoplan.vercel.app
GitHub: github.com/[your-username]/tennoplan
Ko-fi: ko-fi.com/tennoplan

## Current Stack
- Pure HTML + CSS + JavaScript (single file: index.html)
- No frameworks, no build tools, no npm packages
- Data: warframestat.us public API (live) + inline JS fallback data
- Storage: localStorage only — no backend, no database, no accounts
- Hosting: Vercel (auto-deploys from GitHub main branch)

## File Structure
tennoplan/
├── index.html        # Entire app — HTML, CSS, and JS in one file
├── tasks.json        # Manual fallback data (mostly unused, inline now)
├── vercel.json       # Vercel routing config
├── .cursorrules      # This file
└── tennoplan-logo.svg

## Architecture Rules
- Keep everything in index.html until the file exceeds ~1000 lines
- All task data is defined inline in the JS as const arrays
- State is saved to localStorage under key 'wf-tracker-v2'
- Weekly reset key is calculated from UTC Monday 00:00
- API calls use apiFetch() helper with 8 second timeout and silent fallback
- Never add npm packages or build steps without discussing first

## API
Base URL: https://api.warframestat.us/pc
Language param: ?language=en
Currently used endpoints:
- /nightwave — live Nightwave acts
- /voidTrader — Baro Ki'Teer status
- /sortie — daily sortie stages
- /archonHunt — weekly Archon Hunt missions
- /fissures — active Void Fissures
- /arbitration — current Arbitration mission

## Coding Style
- Vanilla JS only — no jQuery, no React, no frameworks
- Functions are small and single purpose
- CSS uses custom properties (--bg, --accent, --gold etc)
- Dark theme only for now
- All API calls are fire-and-forget with .catch(() => {}) silent fallback
- No console.log left in production code

## What NOT to do
- Do not suggest npm install or package.json changes
- Do not suggest splitting into multiple files yet
- Do not add TypeScript
- Do not add a backend or database
- Do not suggest React or any framework yet
- Do not add authentication of any kind

## Current Features (already built)
- Weekly reset countdown timer (UTC Monday)
- Search Pulse budget planner (5 pulses, allocate across EDA/Netracells/Temporal)
- Weekly activity cards (Archon Hunt, EDA, Temporal, Circuit, Syndicate)
- Daily activity cards (Sortie, Netracell, Syndicate Dailies, Void Fissures)
- Live Nightwave acts with standing tracker and progress bar
- Live Baro Ki'Teer status and timer
- Live Sortie stages
- Live Archon Hunt missions
- Live Void Fissures by tier with timers
- Live Arbitration mission
- Ko-fi support button (ko-fi.com/tennoplan)
- All progress saved to localStorage, resets weekly automatically

## Next Planned Features
- Steel Path honors rotation
- Invasions tracker
- UI overhaul with tabs/sections
- Mobile responsiveness polish
- Eventually: Electron desktop app wrapper

## Context for AI
When helping with this project:
- Always give targeted code snippets, never full file rewrites
- Always specify exactly where in the file to paste code
- Use Ctrl+F find references to locate insertion points
- Keep changes minimal and surgical
- Test suggestions against the existing apiFetch() and renderCards() patterns
